{"tid":2227973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子元朗街頭毀五星旗被捕","createTime":"2020-10-03T08:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T05:12:11.000Z","uid":44209,"like":4,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"08ce53016bbe3a723418292e53dcdbc7b2cd3ba4","tid":2227973,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T08:12:04.000Z","msg":"元朗分區特遣隊人員今日（3日）凌晨約1時進行反罪惡巡邏，於安寧路發現一名37歲本地男子將懸掛在路旁的五星旗及區旗破壞，並棄置在路上及附近河道，以及盜去一面區旗。警員隨即上前截停該名男子，並以涉嫌刑事毀壞、侮辱國旗及盜竊拘捕他，帶署扣留調查，案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方再次提醒市民，侮辱國旗乃刑事罪行。 根據《國旗及國徽條例》，任何人公開及故意以焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗或國徽，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，最高可判處監禁3年。"},{"pid":"b22e0743b600e56a981d488d48d256e59bc61018","tid":2227973,"uid":44209,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VdVS0x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VdVS0x.gif&h=7eefe592&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d539a62f53faa8c7955e5fbbd5463a87f2c4912","tid":2227973,"uid":187201,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"啲旗非法掛出黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ebd088fb54cf79bf3080f557aab1e40cf31cf3","tid":2227973,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93ea8fc356e1a6408f00645dd0c1333452e3d19","tid":2227973,"uid":44209,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"36ebd088fb54cf79bf3080f557aab1e40cf31cf3","tid":2227973,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFWcVfe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFWcVfe.gif&h=f8c376e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29aab199fe78233b4444fc44ec16412b4